Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:01.93,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You have visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:04.52,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:06.23,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:09.61,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Please let us accompany you, \Nat least during the Waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:12.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Can you arrange for class upgrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:17.62,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,You can simply get it done at another \Ncountry's dragon hourglass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:19.99,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We won't get there before the Wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:24.25,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Once all the Waves are repelled,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:29.59,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,you'll go back to your own world, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:33.72,main,Mir,0000,0000,0000,,The next Wave is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.59,main,Mir,0000,0000,0000,,Will the heroes be able to overcome it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:49.06,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.69,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the potions, I also packed \Nsome leftover weapons I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:56.16,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,They'll make for decent backups.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:57.70,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:02.29,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm impressed you managed \Nto stock up on so much medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Even this may not be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling what'll \Nhappen during the Wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:12.34,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,If you're being that careful, \Nyou'll be fine this time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:15.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Hold out your hand, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.09,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:20.01,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:25.43,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's imbued with a spell to\N boost your mana generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.77,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Not much of a present for a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:29.27,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Boost my mana generation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:30.90,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:32.36,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:38.16,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Only she gets one? No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.57,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:48.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It'll increase your agility.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.88,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's very cute, Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.75,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:56.47,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Thank you, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:02.14,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And a hairpin won't fall \Noff when you transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:07.56,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,What brought this accessory-making spree on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:10.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's just to boost their stats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.44,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Really, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:13.73,main,Ake,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.32,sign_3350_39_Register_the_Ake,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(398,1)\blur3}Register the Ake Squad\N to be teleported with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now you'll be teleported along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.20,main,Ake,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:34.25,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We're off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.88,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.09,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll be waiting in the shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.26,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Y'all better come back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:40.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.24,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,OP Card,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,645)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:20.32,sign_5367_37_Lullaby_at_Dawn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(486,682)}Catastrophe Returns
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.70,main,SoldierB,0000,0000,0000,,The other villagers have already evacuated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.08,main,SoldierB,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:43.87,main,V,0000,0000,0000,,G-Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:48.09,main,SoldierB,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it for the evacuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.17,main,SoldierA,0000,0000,0000,,That took a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.46,main,SoldierA,0000,0000,0000,,We should get back and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:04:59.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:01.10,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.31,main,SoldierA,0000,0000,0000,,So strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.81,main,SoldierA,0000,0000,0000,,They took down a lizardman in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:13.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Stay alert! There are more monsters around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.57,main,Bo,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,She killed them in one hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:30.75,main,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for your \Nhelp before, Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:32.92,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that same old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:45.85,main,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I'm all better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.18,main,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.31,main,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.27,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:54.65,main,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Small fry like these are no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:06:00.74,main,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,I swear on these fists, which fought many a \Nformidable foe back when I was an adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:04.03,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did I feed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:05.20,main,Ake,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.70,main,Ake,0000,0000,0000,,We've finished evacuating the villagers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:09.66,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.42,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now focus on keeping the enemy out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:19.21,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three whole hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.05,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,What are those guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:24.30,main,Ake,0000,0000,0000,,Please go, Sir Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:30.06,main,Ake,0000,0000,0000,,Putting an end to the Wave as soon as \Npossible will also help the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:31.27,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:36.11,main,Gran,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the village to ol' Gran \Nhere and these whippersnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.57,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:40.11,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't push your luck, Gran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia, Filo, we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.66,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.66,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:00.84,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:06.30,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What a big ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.10,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:20.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:25.87,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,They're on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:30.12,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,I told them attacking that statue and \Nspawning the Soul Eater came first, but nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:32.16,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,How irresponsible can they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:19.75,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Motoyasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:21.67,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,We need to take out the skeleton first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:23.42,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,No, the kraken comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:25.91,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Eater won't spawn otherwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:27.18,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.01,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You morons...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:29.14,top,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:30.14,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be bickering!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.17,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.39,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Go defend some village or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.81,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.23,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,An incompetent hero who can't fight should...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.71,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Who's really incompetent here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:46.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't put an end to \Nthe Wave, the monsters will keep coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:48.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I can't defend a village like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:50.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:56.83,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of working together, you three \Nare doing whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:02.44,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose, all the villagers \Nwill die, and so will you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Quit thinking this is some game already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:08.34,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.51,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm hitting the skeleton \Nto spawn the Soul Eater!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:11.97,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:15.06,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You killed it earlier, but nothing spawned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:17.23,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,We need to kill it several times!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:18.73,top,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.44,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,These morons...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.69,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have any special \Nparameters or resistances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:29.36,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a way to spawn a Soul Eater\N other than killing that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:35.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia! Cast light magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:37.58,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Light? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:38.58,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.50,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,As source of thy power, I order thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:48.49,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Decipher the laws of nature and \Nilluminate my surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.43,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Fast Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:57.64,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the shadow by its feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:14.95,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,So many of them were hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.12,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:20.21,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Eaters are spawning \Nfrom all over the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:33.11,sign_16877_133_Missing,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(271,1)}Dimensional Soul Eater
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:42.07,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Thunderbolt Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:44.82,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:47.99,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.91,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,It's sturdier than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:58.04,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Are our attacks even affecting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:00.54,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get nowhere with only \Nlightning-element attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo, cast wind magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:05.38,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.89,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Fast Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:19.23,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Or else it'll use a powerful skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:19.98,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:25.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia, Filo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:49.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:50.59,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.93,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,High Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:00.19,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Can't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:25.17,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,This strategy will kill it eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.09,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:32.18,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,If we take too long,\N the village will be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.86,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,He's not taking damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.11,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain. We have to kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.32,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use the Rage Shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:51.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:04.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I am your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:09.13,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I will follow you through \Nfire and brimstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:14.93,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Raphtalia \Nif anything goes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:20.81,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remain by your side until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:29.11,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Rage Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:45.21,italics,Rot,0000,0000,0000,,...will pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:55.26,italics,Rot,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:14.11,italics,Rot,0000,0000,0000,,For humiliating me by defeating \Nme as a puny human...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:21.87,italics,Rot,0000,0000,0000,,And for humiliating me by taking my \Nbones and turning me into a tool...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:25.83,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the dragon zombie\NI absorbed back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:28.04,italics,Rot,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:30.50,italics,Rot,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.80,sign_24244_172_Growth_affected_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Growth affected by Zombie Dragon Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,"Grow up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:48.06,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,A seething rage...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:50.48,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the flame from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:53.57,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's his hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.88,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.13,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:18.51,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo's being affected by \Nthe dragon zombie, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:38.91,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,He's basically a wild beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:42.03,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't how a hero is supposed to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:44.75,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you people \Nstanding around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.58,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,H-How dare you, demi-human!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:51.46,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama is fighting in our place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.88,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:57.88,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,If only I weren't so useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:00.97,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,If only I were stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.31,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have to put him through this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:11.11,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You have the power, so why won't you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:14.27,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,How can you call yourselves the \Nworld's heroes like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:20.95,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:25.45,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.29,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:36.46,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have to help that bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:40.01,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you, but we have no \Nother choice right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:41.34,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:45.06,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama? You mustn't help the Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.43,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Can {\i1}you{\i0} kill that thing, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:04.78,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:08.25,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Very cool, but you're not \Ndoing much damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.42,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:27.81,italics,Rot,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:30.06,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:33.81,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Settle down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:37.32,italics,Rot,0000,0000,0000,,I will make you pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:47.16,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:58.17,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I swear to protect Raphtalia, Filo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:01.97,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,and all the villagers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:24.57,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:39.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Change Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:47.68,doublespeak,N,0000,0000,0000,,Within this virgin of cold ore, who shall \Nswallow even your screams with her embrace,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:51.68,doublespeak,N,0000,0000,0000,,suffer in anguish as your entire \Nbody is stabbed and skewered!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:54.85,doublespeak,N,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:48.61,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:52.20,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:55.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama! Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:58.62,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:00.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.93,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what the Shield is capable of?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.68,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,It's basically a cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.18,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Things will be different next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.02,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:19.85,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Sore loser, much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:22.48,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not it, Filo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:27.65,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I'm, uh, just saying I could've one-shotted \Nthat thing if I'd gotten serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:29.03,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:30.57,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.57,0:20:32.41,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu never lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.58,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:43.42,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.25,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't in the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:59.56,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,How very disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:14.07,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,You have trouble with weaklings like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:18.12,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really the heroes who hold \Nthe world's fate in their hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:26.26,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,It seems only one man here is \Nworthy of even being called a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:29.02,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:32.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to introduce yourself \Nbefore asking for someone' name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.35,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:36.29,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:41.99,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to consider me your enemy, hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:43.68,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.04,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Naofumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:49.52,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:54.88,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we begin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:58.24,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,the true battle of this Wave?
